    "body": "Hi @godfreyhobbs! It looks like a bug in our docs generation. That page shouldn't exist; note that `Destructible` is not in [the sidebar for 2.0.0](https://openzeppelin.org/api/docs/crowdsale_Crowdsale.html).\r\n\r\nPlease take a look at https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/pull/1254 for the reasons for removing `Destructible`.\r\n\r\n> I think it is a useful tool especially when doing iterations on testnet.\r\n\r\nThis is a very interesting point. We removed the feature because we consider it dangerous on mainnet, but I can see how it can be useful in some testing workflows. I'll keep this in mind but unfortunately the other point is kind of a deal breaker.",
